Hi Sara:


Below is an example of language we are currently using for common pricing.

We have been tailoring the language for each deal to specify which indices

the deals are priced on, however, we would like to have language that is

generic (i.e. Pricing to be effective only on the days when the applicable

indices are published, etc.).  Will you help us develop language for this?

Thank you!


Common Pricing:


Pricing to be effective only on the days when both the IPE is open and Platts

publish their dated Brent assessment.
